"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1166875","Department for Education","false","2019-10-31","<p>The Department does not hold centrally information on how many and what proportion of pupils in England aged 11, 16 and 18 do not have entry Level 3 levels of literacy nor the information on the number of secondary school leavers in England who do not have Level 3 levels of literacy.</p><p> </p>","Bognor Regis and Littlehampton","Nick Gibb","6319","2019-10-31T17:05:01.883Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1166875/answer","Biography information for Nick Gibb","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1166875/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1166875/answer",,,,,"60","Education","Education","2019-10-28","Pupils: Literacy","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Education, how many and what proportion of pupils in England aged (a) 11 (b) 16 and (c) 18 did not have Entry Level 3 levels of literacy in each of the last five years for which figures are available.","false","Biography information for Mr Jeremy Hunt","South West Surrey","Mr Jeremy Hunt","6318"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1166876","Department for Education","false","2019-10-31","<p>The Department does not hold centrally information on how many and what proportion of pupils in England aged 11, 16 and 18 do not have entry Level 3 levels of literacy nor the information on the number of secondary school leavers in England who do not have Level 3 levels of literacy.</p><p> </p>","Bognor Regis and Littlehampton","Nick Gibb","6318","2019-10-31T17:05:01.93Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1166876/answer","Biography information for Nick Gibb","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1166876/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1166876/answer",,,,,"60","Education","Education","2019-10-28","School Leaving: Literacy","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Education, what estimate his Department has made of the number of secondary school leavers in England who did not have Entry Level 3 levels of literacy in each of the last five years for which figures are available.","false","Biography information for Mr Jeremy Hunt","South West Surrey","Mr Jeremy Hunt","6319"
